WEBVTT

00:13:29.112 --> 00:13:32.315
then their voices will always
feel overwhelming.

00:13:33.488 --> 00:13:38.407
But if we accept instead
that learning is sometimes messy,

00:13:38.431 --> 00:13:42.010
that it requires opportunities
to brainstorm and mess up

00:13:42.034 --> 00:13:43.555
and try again,

00:13:43.579 --> 00:13:46.654
that our kids dislike chaos
and want to learn

00:13:46.678 --> 00:13:48.659
when they come to school,

00:13:48.683 --> 00:13:52.409
then we can set up schools
to facilitate that kind of learning.

00:13:53.015 --> 00:13:55.826
So do me a favor and close
your eyes for a second

00:13:55.850 --> 00:14:00.238
and imagine schools
where teachers are thought partners,